Second Department,

May, 1950.

(May 1, 1950.) Josephine Ajaeb, Appellant, v. James Ajaeb, Respondent.

Motion referred to the court that rendered the decision. Present — Nolan, P. J., Johnston, Sneed, Wenzel and MaeCrate, JJ. Motion for reargument denied, without costs. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Nolan, P. J., Carswell, Johnston, Adel and Sneed, JJ. [See 276 App. Div. 1094.]
